地落去<br />\n咁就更加無可能平息到 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一星期一示威行街 》黑警繼續封路封鐵搞死經濟<br />\n禁制令不斷出黑警不斷打 》嚇走外資<br />\n<br />\n到最後出條禁制令唔比人示威 出街怎至係上網 <br />\n或者更多更荒謬嘅禁制令 全部通通都係毒藥<br />\n毒死我哋同事都毒死成個香港所有嘅行業"},{"pid":"fe66444870d80b6916fb915e7f4827de4e4b55ed","tid":1687130,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3bd2b12679ea92c56f94ec0497d5439f86b5db","tid":1687130,"uid":329466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:24:10.000Z","msg":"長期戰"},{"pid":"8399e377350d179b165cff3dce31b99fbe7222d4","tid":1687130,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:24:39.000Z","msg":"但要大家堅持"},{"pid":"66ec49df1a7bc7b5c446bdbc75a58d8dc155c245","tid":1687130,"uid":181088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:29:05.000Z","msg":"其實由焦土派打開左潘多拉的盒子果刻<br />\n我地就只係得2個字<br />\n<br />\n攬炒<br />\n<br />\n願 我地有日係香城online到<br />\n將獅鳥同長龍 變成祭品<br />\n換取最後既召喚獸&mdash;鳳凰"},{"pid":"125bc60e6e4f718bf9a976205bc9b8b9e0d38e59","tid":1687130,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:37:41.000Z","msg":"香港會死<br />\n但政權唔會死"},{"pid":"87f701e73ecda9cdab921df327ab7c65682197c6","tid":1687130,"uid":7738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8399e377350d179b165cff3dce31b99fbe7222d4","tid":1687130,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:24:39.000Z","msg":"但要大家堅持"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:40:33.000Z","msg":"政權就係同你賭<br />\n邊個堅持到最後<br />\n<br />\n經濟收皮先<br />\n定停止示威活動先"},{"pid":"1956cefb3ea329612a24985bf0860c7210987ec3","tid":1687130,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87f701e73ecda9cdab921df327ab7c65682197c6","tid":1687130,"uid":7738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8399e377350d179b165cff3dce31b99fbe7222d4","tid":1687130,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":